    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062509_17_1174-1259",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "1174-1259",
      "markText": "我总是在极力避免写女性或是和女性相关的话题。不知道为什么，这类话题会让我觉得很不舒服、很荒谬。女人并不是某种特殊的生物种群，所以我不明白为什么她们可以形成一个单独的话题。",
      "totalCount": 476,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062509&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=1174&rangeEnd=1259",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/48432de0813ab7eeag019fa6?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=1174&rangeEnd=1259"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062509_22_2084-2113",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "2084-2113",
      "markText": "勇敢并不意味着不害怕。它意味着尽管害怕，却仍要做该做之事。",
      "totalCount": 456,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062509&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=2084&rangeEnd=2113",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/48432de0813ab7eeag019fa6?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=2084&rangeEnd=2113"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062509_4_917-929",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "917-929",
      "markText": "人们爱我，却并不理解我。",
      "totalCount": 400,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062509&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=917&rangeEnd=929",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/48432de0813ab7eeag019fa6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=917&rangeEnd=929"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062509_4_771-785",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "771-785",
      "markText": "自由首先是义务，其次才是权利",
      "totalCount": 390,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062509&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=771&rangeEnd=785",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/48432de0813ab7eeag019fa6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=771&rangeEnd=785"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062509_34_2916-3054",
      "chapterUid": 34,
      "range": "2916-3054",
      "markText": "战争是一场推迟了二十年的人工流产，但那些不能够接受人工流产的人，却接受了战争的存在。",
      "totalCount": 384,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062509&chapterUid=34&rangeStart=2916&rangeEnd=3054",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/48432de0813ab7eeag019fa6?chapterUid=34&rangeStart=2916&rangeEnd=3054"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062509_17_5417-5442",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "5417-5442",
      "markText": "束缚固然可怕无情，但以错误的方式诠释自由亦是如此。",
      "totalCount": 380,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062509&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=5417&rangeEnd=5442",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/48432de0813ab7eeag019fa6?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=5417&rangeEnd=5442"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062509_32_4672-4701",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "4672-4701",
      "markText": "我从未想过要功成名就，是成功找上我，并专横野蛮地将我占据。",
      "totalCount": 374,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062509&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=4672&rangeEnd=4701",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/48432de0813ab7eeag019fa6?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=4672&rangeEnd=4701"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062509_5_669-724",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "669-724",
      "markText": "在国外，每当人们问我是哪里人时，我始终回答“我是佛罗伦萨人”，而不是“意大利人”。因为这是两个完全不同的概念。",
      "totalCount": 368,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062509&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=669&rangeEnd=724",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/48432de0813ab7eeag019fa6?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=669&rangeEnd=724"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062509_32_5854-5944",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "5854-5944",
      "markText": "令人们讨厌的并非我的外表，而是我骨子中散发出的孤独。人们能够从我身上感知到一种不需要任何人的孤独，以及对自我的坚信。假如一个人没有自信，不能满足自身需要，那他就体会不到孤独的快乐。",
      "totalCount": 341,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062509&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=5854&rangeEnd=5944",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/48432de0813ab7eeag019fa6?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=5854&rangeEnd=5944"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062509_29_4935-4965",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "4935-4965",
      "markText": "为什么我说自己深爱着阿莱科斯？因为我允许他闯进我孤独的人生。",
      "totalCount": 336,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062509&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=4935&rangeEnd=4965",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/48432de0813ab7eeag019fa6?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=4935&rangeEnd=4965"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062509_32_7367-7405",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "7367-7405",
      "markText": "我感谢每一位当我不能陪伴在阿莱科斯身边时，给他带去哪怕是片刻欢愉和喜悦的人。",
      "totalCount": 324,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062509&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=7367&rangeEnd=7405",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/48432de0813ab7eeag019fa6?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=7367&rangeEnd=7405"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062509_33_3276-3355",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "3276-3355",
      "markText": "我觉得婚姻已经是过时的东西了。在我的书《给一个未出生孩子的信》中，我曾经写道：女人一定要做母亲的想法已经是老一辈人的东西了。现在我要加一句，婚姻也是老古董了。",
      "totalCount": 315,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062509&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=3276&rangeEnd=3355",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/48432de0813ab7eeag019fa6?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=3276&rangeEnd=3355"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062509_17_4023-4093",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "4023-4093",
      "markText": "他甚至还问：“跟我说说，日本女人真的会裸着进浴池帮我们洗澡吗？香港女人真的很容易就会跟人上床吗？印度女人真的知道一百四十六种做爱的方法吗？”",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062509&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=4023&rangeEnd=4093",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/48432de0813ab7eeag019fa6?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=4023&rangeEnd=4093"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062509_5_3423-3453",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3423-3453",
      "markText": "不过也有人说，祖父之所以娶祖母，只是为了报复抛弃他的曾祖母。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062509&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3423&rangeEnd=3453",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/48432de0813ab7eeag019fa6?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3423&rangeEnd=3453"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062509_11_1517-1559",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1517-1559",
      "markText": "“记者的首要职责是永不厌烦自己的工作，其次是不能害怕，第三是不能马虎对待任何事情。”",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062509&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1517&rangeEnd=1559",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/48432de0813ab7eeag019fa6?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1517&rangeEnd=1559"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062509_10_2752-2865",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "2752-2865",
      "markText": "我不曾为钱写作，也永远不会为钱写作。永远不会！",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062509&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2752&rangeEnd=2865",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/48432de0813ab7eeag019fa6?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2752&rangeEnd=2865"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062509_4_375-404",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "375-404",
      "markText": "我很晚才开始明白自己的重要性，明白自己对很多人意味着什么。",
      "totalCount": 242,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062509&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=375&rangeEnd=404",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/48432de0813ab7eeag019fa6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=375&rangeEnd=404"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062509_8_4294-4321",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "4294-4321",
      "markText": "当时我认为，学生属于脑力劳动者，也应该获得相应的工资。",
      "totalCount": 242,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062509&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4294&rangeEnd=4321",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/48432de0813ab7eeag019fa6?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4294&rangeEnd=4321"
    },
    {
